  "prompt": "How do I add question details digitally on Quora?",
  "response": "To add question details digitally on Quora, follow these steps:\n\n1. **Log In to Quora**:\n   - Open the Quora website or app and log in to your account.\n\n2. **Start Asking a Question**:\n   - Click on the \"Add Question\" button, which is usually located at the top of the homepage or in the navigation bar.\n\n3. **Type Your Question**:\n   - Enter your question in the text box provided. Make sure your question is clear and concise.\n\n4. **Add Question Details**:\n   - Below the question text box, you will find an option to \"Add Question Details\" or \"Add more context to your question.\" Click on this option.\n   - In the details section, provide additional information, context, or background that can help others understand your question better. This can include examples, specific scenarios, or any relevant information.\n\n5. **Choose Topics**:\n   - Quora will prompt you to add relevant topics to your question. This helps your question reach the right audience. You can select from existing topics or create a new one if necessary.\n\n6. **Review and Post**:\n   - Review your question and the details you\u2019ve added to ensure everything is clear and accurate.\n   - Click the \"Add Question\" button to post your question on Quora.\n\nBy adding detailed context, you increase the chances of receiving accurate and helpful answers from the Quora community.",
